#: mb/cli.py:377
msgid ""
"Finds non-JPEG bytes under .jpg/.jpeg names in class source trees (same discovery as convert), writes corrected "
"JPEGs, and removes stale copies under CONVERTED and small_images_review only after a successful write. Animated GIFs "
